title: Hour 1 - NFL Market Correction
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NFL Market Correction
description:
Dan Patrick highlights a few NFL teams that may overachieve on their expectations this season and look at how the spotlight continues to shift across the NFL. Why does Russell Wilson get sacked so much? Plus, Dan reacts to Albert Pujols' hot streak over the last month.
